{
  "stem": "18770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you had asked me in my 20s, 30s who I was, the first thing I would have said then was an artist because I had to have a real struggle to find and establish that identity in a family where no one had ever been an artist, and there was only fear and negativity about it.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that would have been the first thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had developed my own political conscience as a kid, going from somebody who refused to read books.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's interesting for a writer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I only would read comic books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was the despair of my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would only read comic books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then one summer when I couldn't get my comic books and was forced to begin reading, I went to a library and took Jack London out of the library and went in one incredible summer from Jack London to Arthur Koestler to John Dos Passos and became a self-styled leftist, socialist, communist, but totally of my own making.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, really struck-- 16 years old, totally struck by the incredible injustices in the world, and how-- you know, I'd go to a movie.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they'd show a newsreel, and say, and the latest fashions from France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would sit there saying fashions from France when millions are starving?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that kind of feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And briefly, briefly, at that young age, I found myself moving towards the American Labor Party, which was really a quasi wing of the Communist Party under disguise.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it wasn't so much that it was communist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I found that early on that I did not like organizations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I did not like organizational thinking because they all had their own orthodoxies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was not-- you know, I didn't like orthodoxies.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
